<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَجَانِبْ الْكِبْرَ يَا مِسْكِينُ وَالْعُجُبِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَارْضَ التَّوَاضُعَ خُلَقًا إِنَّهُ خُلُقُ الـ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَخْيَارِ فَاقْتَدْ بِهِمْ تَنْجُو مِنْ الْوَصَبِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَخَالِفِ النَّفْسَ وَاسْتَشْعِرْ عَدَاوَتَهَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَارْفُضْ هَوَاهَا وَمَا تَخْتَارُهُ تُصِبِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِنْ دَعَتْكَ إِلَى حَظٍّ بِشَهْوَتِهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَاشْرَحْ لَهَا غِبَّ مَا فِيهِ مِنَ التَّعَبِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَازْهَدْ بِقَلْبِكَ فِي الدَّارِ الَّتِي فَتَنَتْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>طَوَائِفًا فَرَأَوْهَا غَايَةَ الطَّلَبِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَنَافَسُوهَا وَأَعْطَوْهَا قَوَالِبَهُمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مَعَ الْقُلُوبِ فَيَا للهِ مِنْ عَجَبِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَهِيَ الَّتِي صَغُرَتْ قَدْرًا وَمَا وَزَنَتْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عِنْدَ الإِلَهِ جَنَاحًا فَالْحَرِيصُ غَبِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَخُذْ بَلاغَكَ مِنْ دُنْيَاكَ وَاسْعَ بِهِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سَعْيَ الْمَجْدِ إِلَى مَوْلاكَ وَاحْتَسِبِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَاعْلَمْ بِأَنَّ الَّذِي يَبْتَاعَ عَاجِلَهُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بِآجِلٍ مِنْ نَعِيمٍ دَائِمٍ يَخِبِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِنْ وَجَدْتَ فَوَاسِ الْمَعْوِزِينَ تَفِضْ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>عَلَيْكَ مِنْ رَبِّكَ الأَرْزَاقُ فَاحْتَسِبِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَإِنْ بُلِيتَ بِفَقْرٍ فَارْضَ مُكْتَفِيًا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>باللهِ مِنْ رَبِّكَ الْفَضْلَ وَارْتَقَبِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَاتْلُ الْقُرْآنَ بِقَلْبٍ حَاضِرٍ وَجَلٍ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>